<p id="p6">On NPC XL, Federico, John, and Brendon share what they do when they’re not obsessing over handheld consoles.</p>
<h2 id="comfort-zone"><a href="https://www.macstories.net/comfort-zone/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Comfort Zone</a></h2>
<p id="p7">Matt’s on his own for this one, as Chris and Niléane managed to both get sick at the same time. Fear not; we get to rant and rave about the latest “Xbox”!</p>
<p id="p8">On Cozy Zone, we roast each other’s backpacks. One’s all black, one’s full of color, and the other is just a mess.</p>
<h2 id="macstories-unwind"><a href="https://www.macstories.net/unwind/" rel="noopener noreferrer">MacStories Unwind</a></h2>
